ser_id";s:2:"15";s:6:"handle";s:14:"Hans_Von_Quake";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"905";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"RubyG";s:4:"text";s:86:"I appreciate that you make no illusion that you and Omega are not on the best of terms";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404186205";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#eae0aa";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14041862129";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#efed72";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:761126;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"761126";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Dimitri";s:4:"text";s:952:"Firstly; http://mlpnwrp.org/Site+Rules[br]Roleplay Guidelines and The Prime Directive (Equestria Side Only). &quot;Please keep in mind that the Equestria side of NewWorlds is supposed to correlate with the show, ergo, please keep all activity there in the &#039;spirit of the show&#039;. What this essentially means is that if you can imagine your thing happening in the show, it&#039;s probably okay. If you&#039;re not sure, please ask a guide. Note: If you feel you need death and/or destruction in your backstory to make it work, it&#039;s probably a good idea to talk to staff first.[br]Things that happen in your character&#039;s past are not occuring in the show. The closest the show has ever gotten to death is the subtle, non-descript wink of the two stars following the mention of Applejack&#039;s parents. Within the show, hospitals are a place to get better and recover. Not a sad place of death. Maybe a boring place, but not a sad place.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404187082";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14041870848";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:761128;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"761128";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Dimitri";s:4:"text";s:762:"Secondly; http://mlpnwrp.org/Site+Rules[br]Roleplay Guidelines and Death/Bodily Injury. &quot; Overtly graphic and/or violent injury/death will not be permitted. Allusions thereof is permissible but no real details are to be given if/when it occurs.&quot;[br]In further detail, Twilight in season 1 had a piano and the rest of the delivery truck&#039;s things dumped ontop of her. She survived, in a full body cast, but was okay. This is pretty much the exact situation you are gunning for that actually KILLED your character&#039;s SO. Ponies (and not just Pinkie) have been shown to survive this. And then going back to the hospital thing, death is just not dealt with like that. Hospitals and medicine can always make it better within the show&#039;s setting.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404187088";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14041870902";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:761129;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"761129";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Dimitri";s:4:"text";s:252:"I do not believe any of this has been approved/talked past a guide. If you&#039;re gonna involve death or grevious bodily injury or whatever in a character, it&#039;s gonna get scrutinised if you don&#039;t run it through properly. Taken away at worst.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404187092";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#c71d10";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14041870948";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#ffbd16";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:761140;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"761140";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"11";s:6:"handle";s:5:"RubyG";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"777";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Dimitri";s:4:"text";s:144:"Oh, now that I remember it, the funeral with the old guy in 